title: Rodney on the ROQ - [1980] MP3 (Vinyl rip)
description: The first Rodney on the ROQ LP, released by Posh Boy Records in 1980, featuring such bands as Adolescents, Agent Orange, Circle Jerks and more. Never released on CD, so this is a vinyl rip that I downloaded on the internet. You'll hear some crackling sounds. Bitrate is 224 kbps but as I say, the main issue is the background noise from the vinyl. A true punk rock classic and not available anywhere else that I know of.
